      "text": "月ストの年明け最初のライブオファーを急遽もらった\n地上波の正月特番で大々的に生放送をするらしい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I received a sudden offer for Moon Tempest's first live performance of the year.\nIt will be a big live broadcast for a New Year's special program on TV.",
