      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "大事なスタートダッシュになると思う\nその分プレッシャーは大きいけど……どうだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think it will be an important start for us.\nBut‚ there will be a lot of pressure‚ what do you think?",
