      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_01-ktn018.m4a",
      "text": "すみません、ご心配をお掛けして……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm sorry for making you worry…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 160.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "軽い立ち眩みで済んで良かったよ\nでも……ちょっと琴乃らしくないな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's good that it was just a slight dizziness.\nBut… it's not like you‚ Kotono.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 167.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_01-ktn019.m4a",
      "text": "え？　私らしくない……ですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh? Not like me…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 171.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃が体調管理に気を遣ってることは知ってる\nそれなのに倒れそうになるなんて……よっぽどだぞ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I know you're conscious about managing your health.\nDespite that‚ almost collapsing like that… It must have been quite serious.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 179.5866666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_01-ktn020.m4a",
      "text": "そういえば、月ストのみんなも帰る時に\n「無理しないでね」って言ってました……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Speaking of which‚ when the Moon Tempest members left‚\nthey told me \"Don't push yourself too hard\"…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 188.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_01-ktn021.m4a",
      "text": "心配させて、しかも実際に倒れちゃうなんて\nリーダー失格ですね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "To make them worry‚ and actually collapsing…\nIt's a failure as a leader…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 196.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_01-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "活動を続けていればそういうこともある\n反省はして、後はしっかり前を向こう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When you continue your activities‚ these things can happen.\nReflect on it and then focus on moving forward.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 201.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_01-ktn022.m4a",
      "text": "はい……ありがとうございます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes… Thank you very much.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 205.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_01-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "いずれにせよ、気分転換は必要だよな……\n久しぶりに月ストのみんなとゆっくり話したらどうだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In any case‚ you need a change of pace…\nHow about taking your time to talk with the Moon Tempest members?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 213.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_01-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "最近はみんなソロの仕事が多いから\nメンバーで過ごす時間も少なかっただろうし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Lately‚ everyone has been doing solo work‚\nso you haven't spent much time together as a group.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 220.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_01-ktn023.m4a",
      "text": "気分転換に、ゆっくりお話を……そう、ですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Taking time for a change of pace… Yes‚ that sounds good.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 224.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_01-ktn024.m4a",
      "text": "それもいいんですけど、私……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I… I might want to have a relaxed conversation",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 233.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_01-ktn025.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんと\n久しぶりにゆっくり話したい……かも、しれません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "with {user}-san…\nIt's been a while…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 240.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_01-ktn026.m4a",
      "text": "最近は{user}さんも\n凄く忙しそうなので……出来たらでいいんですけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san has been really busy lately‚\nso if it's possible…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 248.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_01-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "そうか。それなら初詣でも一緒にどうだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see. In that case‚ how about going to the shrine together for the first visit of the year?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 253.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_01-ktn027.m4a",
      "text": "えっ！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 258,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_01-koh016.m4a",
      "text": "ライブの成功祈願も兼ねて、ってことで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's for praying for the success of our live performances.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 259.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_01-ktn028.m4a",
      "text": "初詣、ですか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The first visit of the year…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 263.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_01-ktn029.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、そんな風に誘ってもらえるなんて\nなんだか不思議な気分です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sure‚ I'm invited in such a way…\nIt feels strange…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 270.8433333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_01-ktn030.m4a",
      "text": "でも、確かにちょうどいいかもしれませんね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But‚ it might be just right.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 273.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_01-ktn031.m4a",
      "text": "初詣……ぜひ、ご一緒させて下さい\n楽しみにしてますね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The first visit of the year… Please let me join you.\nI'm looking forward to it.",
        "id": ""
      },
